{"body": "Thanks for the feedback.\n\nWhen has having a slightly more verbose way of doing things stoped Rails from providing a helper for better readability? ;)  I'm particularly glad I no longer need to do !string.blank? anymore (and that's actually 1 less character than string.present? !)\n\nWhat don't you like about the API (just out of curiosity, even if this doesn't happen)?\n\nI've run into this a few times and think it would be useful.  It may just be that not many people have gone to the bother of requesting it.\n\nIf you re-open this I'll re-apply to master", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5661103", "created_at": "2012-05-11T20:58:06Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/4759#issuecomment-5661103", "updated_at": "2012-05-11T20:58:06Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 4759, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cheerfulstoic/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cheerfulstoic/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cheerfulstoic/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/cheerfulstoic", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cheerfulstoic/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/cheerfulstoic", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cheerfulstoic/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/1888e77eb90dd84da79b94ce50b6e670?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fe87ee55c4373c75c2d6d4f93c507df9a.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cheerfulstoic/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cheerfulstoic/received_events", "gravatar_id": "1888e77eb90dd84da79b94ce50b6e670", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cheerfulstoic/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "cheerfulstoic", "type": "User", "id": 301415, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cheerfulstoic/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523821c2bd3543c15100e9ee"}, "id": 5661103, "issue_url